The '''urran''' was one of several long sticks used in the sport of [[phrenbi]].<ref name="Socorro">''[[The Black Sands of Socorro]]''</ref>

{{Stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
The urran was introduced in ''[[The Black Sands of Socorro]]'', a [[1997]] sourcebook authored by [[Patricia A. Jackson]] for use with [[West End Games]]' ''[[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game]]''. In the book, the urran was depicted in an illustration by [[Joel Carroll]].<ref name="Socorro" />

